snippet: The authorities on Tuesday were trying to determine whether a driver found dead of a self-inflicted gunshot wound in Memphis is a quadruple amputee wanted after the fatal shooting of his parents in their Orlando, Fla., home.
abstract: Authorities are trying to determine whether driver found dead of self-inflicted wounds in Memphis is quadruple amputee Sean Petrozzino, who is wanted after fatal shooting of his parents in their Orlando home.
lead_paragraph: The authorities on Tuesday were trying to determine whether a driver found dead of a self-inflicted gunshot wound in Memphis is a quadruple amputee wanted after the fatal shooting of his parents in their Orlando, Fla., home.

headline.main: Florida: Amputee Who Killed Himself May Be Wanted in Killings of Parents
headline.print_headline: Florida: Amputee Who Killed Himself May Be Focus in Killings of Parents
